      "body" : "Why use a StringBuffer? Why convert the Integer to a String and then to an Integer and then to an int and then to an Integer again? Why use an array with a single element in it, and why loop over that single-element array when it contains just one element? Why cast the Integers to Objects in the outer loop? There are so many questions here. Is @CodeMadness just a troll account?"
