    "answer_id" : 31992122,
    "question_id" : 718554,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>You can simply copy it to an array:</p>\n\n<pre><code>int[] arr = new int[list.size()];\nfor(int i = 0; i &lt; list.size(); i++) {\n    arr[i] = list.get(i);\n}\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>Not too fancy; but, hey, it works...</p>\n"
