    "answer_id" : 60999431,
    "question_id" : 718554,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>This works nice for me :)</p>\n\n<p>Found at <a href=\"https://www.techiedelight.com/convert-list-integer-array-int/\" rel=\"noreferrer\">https://www.techiedelight.com/convert-list-integer-array-int/</a></p>\n\n<pre><code>import java.util.Arrays;\nimport java.util.List;\n\nclass ListUtil\n{\n    // Program to convert list of integer to array of int in Java\n    public static void main(String args[])\n    {\n        List&lt;Integer&gt; list = Arrays.asList(1, 2, 3, 4, 5);\n\n        int[] primitive = list.stream()\n                            .mapToInt(Integer::intValue)\n                            .toArray();\n\n        System.out.println(Arrays.toString(primitive));\n    }\n}\n</code></pre>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 10535144,
      "reputation" : 11,
      "user_id" : 7763291,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "profile_image" : "https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/35355395eeaa61cd1baf8036c02ba833?s=256&d=identicon&r=PG&f=y&so-version=2",
      "display_name" : "Sherlock",
      "link" : "https://stackoverflow.com/users/7763291/sherlock"
    },
    "is_accepted" : false,
    "score" : 1,
    "last_activity_date" : 1594394028,
    "creation_date" : 1594394028,
    "answer_id" : 62837289,
    "question_id" : 718554,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>Next lines you can find convertion from int[] -&gt; List -&gt; int[]</p>\n<pre><code>   private static int[] convert(int[] arr) {\n        List&lt;Integer&gt; myList=new ArrayList&lt;Integer&gt;();\n        for(int number:arr){\n               myList.add(number);\n            }\n        }\n        int[] myArray=new int[myList.size()];\n        for(int i=0;i&lt;myList.size();i++){\n           myArray[i]=myList.get(i);\n        }\n        return myArray;\n    }\n</code></pre>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 452040,
      "reputation" : 17520,
      "user_id" : 848253,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "accept_rate" : 62,
      "profile_image" : "https://i.sstatic.net/9ODjM.png?s=256",
