    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p><strong>Don't use java stream for this task if time is critical for your task</strong>\n<br />\nIt is slower than using for-each loop. Use the same as:</p>\n<pre><code>    List&lt;Integer&gt; modes = new ArrayList&lt;&gt;();\n    int[] m = new int[modes.size()];\n    for (int i = 0; i &lt; m.length; i++) {\n        m[i] = modes.get(i);\n    }\n</code></pre>\n<p>You can measure it with <em><strong>jmh</strong></em></p>\n"
